OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FLargely dry
OL,6,Fand settled, although rather cloudy,
OL,7,Fespecially across Derbyshire where the
OL,8,Fodd spot of rain is possible.
OL,9,FElsewhere, occasional breaks in the
OL,10,Fcloud will allow for some fine spells.
OL,11,FA warm night for some.
OL,12,
OL,13,CMonday:FRather cloudy initially but
OL,14,Fbrightening up quickly, with spells of
OL,15,Fhazy sunshine widely developing across
OL,16,Fthe region. Becoming warm in the
OL,17,Fafternoon, particularly in the south.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
