OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FA mix
OL,6,Fof cloudy periods and sunny spells.
OL,7,FOccasionally breezy, and remaining
OL,8,Fvery warm or hot in places as
OL,9,Ftemperatures are likely to gradually
OL,10,Fincrease.
